LanguageData.ClashOfRim.GiftDelivery.ConfirmForced:
Force-deliver these items to {TARGET}?

{THINGS}

Forced delivery cannot be rejected, but it is still limited by hostility, online status, raid protection, and forced-delivery cooldown.

